$lang['Similarly, after reaching 9 in Hexadecimal (represented by “F”), we start counting again at 10 (“10”). This pattern continues until we reach 15 (“1F”), at which point we reset back to 0 and begin counting again at 16 (“20”). This might sound confusing at first, but with a little practice, it will become second nature!'] = 'Nya kitu, sanggeus ngahontal 9 dina Hexadecimal (digambarkeun ku &quot;F&quot;), urang mimitian cacah deui dina 10 (&quot;10&quot;). Pola ieu terus dugi ka ngahontal 15 (&quot;1F&quot;), dimana urang ngareset deui ka 0 sareng ngawitan cacah deui dina 16 (&quot;20&quot;). Ieu sigana ngabingungkeun dina mimitina, tapi kalayan latihan sakedik, éta bakal janten alam kadua!';
