$lang['You can use hexadecimal to convert between decimal and binary values. For example, converting 10011011001010 into hexadecimal would result in 0x4F. This means that the value 4F represents the binary number 100110110010110.'] = 'Anjeun tiasa nganggo héksadesimal pikeun ngarobih antara nilai perpuluhan sareng binér. Contona, ngarobah 10011011001010 kana héksadesimal bakal ngahasilkeun 0x4F. Ieu ngandung harti yén nilai 4F ngagambarkeun angka binér 100110110010110.';
$lang['In mathematics and computer science, hexadecimal (also base 16, or hex) is a positional numeral system with a radix, or base, of 16. It uses sixteen distinct symbols, most often the symbols 0–9 to represent values zero to nine, and A, B, C, D, E, F (or alternatively a–f) to represent values ten to fifteen. For example, the hexadecimal number 2AF3 is equal, in decimal, to (2 × 163) + (10 × 162) + (15 × 161) + (3 × 160) , or 10,995.'] = 'Dina matématika jeung élmu komputer, héksadesimal (ogé basa 16, atawa hex) nyaéta sistem numeral posisional kalayan radix, atawa dasar, tina 16. Ieu ngagunakeun genep belas simbol béda, paling sering lambang 0-9 keur ngagambarkeun nilai nol nepi ka salapan. jeung A, B, C, D, E, F (atawa alternatipna a–f) pikeun ngagambarkeun nilai sapuluh nepi ka lima belas. Contona, angka héksadesimal 2AF3 sarua, dina desimal, jeung (2 × 163) + (10 × 162) + (15 × 161) + (3 × 160) , atawa 10.995.';
$lang['Each hexadecimal digit represents four binary digits (bits) (also called a "nibble"), and the primary use of hexadecimal notation is as a human-friendly representation of binary coded values in computing and digital electronics. For example, byte values can range from 0 to 255 (decimal) but may be more conveniently represented as two hexadecimal digits in the range 00 through FF. Hexadecimal is also commonly used to represent computer memory addresses.'] = 'Unggal digit héksadesimal ngagambarkeun opat digit binér (bit) (ogé disebut &quot;nibble&quot;), sarta pamakéan primér notasi héksadesimal nyaéta salaku representasi ramah-manusa tina nilai kode binér dina komputasi jeung éléktronika digital. Contona, nilai bait bisa rupa-rupa ti 0 nepi ka 255 (desimal) tapi bisa jadi leuwih merenah digambarkeun salaku dua digit héksadesimal dina rentang 00 ngaliwatan FF. Hexadecimal ogé ilahar dipaké pikeun ngagambarkeun alamat mémori komputer.';
$lang['Hex is an abbreviation of Hexadecimal, which is based on a base -16 structure and is used for simplifying how instructions to computers are represented. This 16 symbols number system was developed as a means of inhibiting an 8-bit binary number, so data can be encoded into computers effortlessly. It can be imprinted and typed using two different hex digits with each hex digit demonstrating a nibble or perhaps a 4-bits format.'] = 'Hex mangrupikeun singketan tina Hexadecimal, anu dumasar kana struktur dasar -16 sareng dianggo pikeun nyederhanakeun kumaha petunjuk pikeun komputer diwakilan. Sistem angka 16 simbol ieu dikembangkeun pikeun ngahambat angka binér 8-bit, ku kituna data tiasa dikodekeun kana komputer kalayan gampang. Éta tiasa dicitak sareng diketik nganggo dua digit hex anu béda sareng unggal angka hex nunjukkeun nibble atanapi format 4-bit.';
$lang['This number system uses 16 symbols that are represented in a range from 0-9 or A-F. The 0–9 represent numbers up to nine whereas A-F is represented by the numeric 10–15. As compared to the other three types of number systems, the hexadecimal numeral system is considered to be the most effective one.'] = 'Sistim angka ieu ngagunakeun 16 simbol nu digambarkeun dina rentang ti 0-9 atanapi AF. 0–9 ngagambarkeun angka nepi ka salapan sedengkeun AF diwakilan ku angka 10–15. Dibandingkeun jeung tilu tipe séjén sistem wilangan, sistem wilangan héksadesimal dianggap paling éféktif.';
